title.narrative: CN-Guizhou Cultural and Natural Heritage Protection and Development

description.narrative: The project development objective is to assist Guizhou Province in protecting cultural and natural heritage, improving basic infrastructure, and fostering tourism development for the benefit of selected communities (including ethnic minority groups).

condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :PA. Schedule Section I. A1 | Description :Guizhou shall maintain the relative organizations throughout theperiod of implementation of the Project with terms of reference, staffing and other resources acceptable to the Bank. | Frequency:Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA. Schedule Section IV. 1 | Description :Guizhou shall: (a) carry out the project based on the OMCP (b) seekBank#s for prior approval for any amendments to the provisions of the OMCP and, put into effect only upon Bank#s agreement. |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA. Schedule Section IV. 2 | Description :For Ethnic Minority component, Guizhou shall cause a CPMG and a VSG tobe founded at selected minority villages by 09/15/2009 with TOR/staffing /other resources acceptable to the Bank, based on OMCP. |Due Date :15-Sep-2009

Finance Agreement :PA. Schedule Section IV. 6 | Description :Guizhou shall cause the participants to implement Guidance # 30, 2007issued by the GZPPC and the GPG on 11/28/2007 to ensure minorities# interests & benefits. | Frequency :Yearly
